sources.title: BOOTLEGGER'S DRIVE-IN SATURDAY NIGHT - RING OF TERROR & TRAUMA
sources.description: A COMPLETE DVD. Custom menu with poster art and audio. SIMPLE BURN INSTRUCTIONS: Download the zipped folder, open it, extract the VIDEO_TS FOLDER, and burn. This disc contains the movie RING OF TERROR & TRAUMA, along with preview and intermission reels, laid out to play like an old drive-in show.
